titles.title: To extend the temporary suspension of duty on 4-Chloro-3,5-dinitro-alpha,alpha,alpha-trifluorotoluene.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

bill.summary: 4/24/2012--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend the temporary suspension of duty on 4-Chloro-3,5-dinitro-,,-trifluorotoluene.
